@startuml
' Simple vector DB overview for report usage

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
left to right direction

title Vector Database Overview (Chroma + Hybrid Retrieval)

actor "User" as User

rectangle "Workflow + KB" as Workflow {
  component "Approved Documents\n(KB markdown)" as KBDocs
}

database "Chroma Vector Store\n(databases/vector_store/chroma)" as Chroma
cloud "Ollama Runtime\nlocalhost:11434" as Ollama

rectangle "Knowledge Chat" as Chat {
  component "Query Embedding" as QEmbed
  component "Vector Search" as VSearch
  component "Answer + Sources" as Answer
}

Workflow --> Chroma : Reindex approved docs
Workflow --> Ollama : Generate chunk embeddings

User --> QEmbed : Ask question
QEmbed --> Ollama : /api/embeddings
QEmbed --> VSearch
VSearch --> Chroma : Similarity query
VSearch --> Answer

note right of Chroma
Stores vectorized chunks
for semantic retrieval.
end note

note bottom of Workflow
Approved KB content is converted to vectors
and stored in Chroma.
end note

@enduml
